headline: Citizens Bank, N.A. Announces Redemption of Senior Notes
summary: Citizens Bank, N.A. today announced the redemption on January 27, 2025 all of its outstanding $350,000,000 aggregate principal amount 5.284% Fixed/Floating Rate Senior Notes due January 26, 2026 ....
